{"tid":2432590,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【Hello Kitty】真人版電影籌備兩年終開拍　由日裔巴西導演操刀","createTime":"2021-03-04T12:17:32.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-04T12:37:22.000Z","uid":46678,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"47cfb338c49c0b111b67e46bfd4e0dfb04ee0ab2","tid":2432590,"uid":46678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T12:17:32.000Z","msg":"華納兄弟在2019年宣布旗下的新線影業（New Line Cinema）取得Hello Kitty的電影版權後，之後就再沒有傳出過新消息。近日外國傳媒《Deadline》報道，華納兄弟終於找到真人版《Hello Kitty》電影的導演人選。有指真人版電影的做法將會同《Tom &amp; Jerry大電影》（Tom and Jerry）一樣，是一部真人動畫電影。<br />\n<br />\n據報道指出，電視動畫《DC超級英雄女孩》美國女導演Jennifer Coyle將聯同短片《心腦交戰》日裔巴西導演松田李歐（Leo Matsuda）聯合執導；至於編劇方面，則由Lindsey Beer負責撰寫劇本。她近年獲得不少編劇機會，手上更有7個劇本需要處理，其中包括《狂野時速》全女班的外傳電影《M.A.S.K.: Mobile Armored Strike Kommand》。<br />\n<br />\n對於有幸獲邀成為真人版《Hello Kitty》電影導演，松田李歐認為他雖然在巴西長大，但同樣被Hello Kitty所吸引：「我與日本的家人在巴西長大，但我被與眾不同的Hello Kitty所包圍，這提醒我們可以有所不同。我好高興可以與Jennifer、Flynn Picture Company及新線影業一起開發這個全球最受歡迎的角色，並進一步擴充有關Hello Kitty的故事，這是一次難得的機會。」<br />\n<br />\n支那01唔po lin<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Q9C9vmP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQ9C9vmP.jpg&h=78d10987&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LW0rxAs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLW0rxAs.jpg&h=f6c47a40&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9441657b78e799d48fe47cb674ef1873a37087e9","tid":2432590,"uid":46678,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T12:19:40.000Z","msg":"證明hello kitty真係咩產品都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n家下有埋真人電影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f57667398189a41b5bf3325c6b6a8f7762bd3fcc","tid":2432590,"uid":10300,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T12:24:22.000Z","msg":"以為hello kitty 案"},{"pid":"a32fb3ee231216c8f8b19ae04767228dd33d64b3","tid":2432590,"uid":143241,"lik